  "thesis": "Before an agent receives tools, data, spend, or production access, InferenceAtlas prepares a Trust Receipt, DecisionPacket, Packet Diff, Packet Outcome Memo, Agent Access Decision Brief, and Proof Health report showing what can move, what stays blocked, whether the agent is eligible for this class of access, how risk posture changes across scenarios, what proof is missing, what may drift, who must review, and what validation comes next.",
